ping means smooth gameplay, while high ping causes delays and lags. Ping=E2=
=80=91test.net is more advanced than the standard ping command because it c=
hecks latency for both small and large packets, revealing issues such as pa=
cket fragmentation that normal tests can=E2=80=99t detect.</p><p>Low ping i=
